{"tid":1025333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所羅門群島海域尋獲二戰日艦比叡號","createTime":"2019-02-17T09:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T10:17:13.000Z","uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"227f012e4ac31a42a99ef86343876fc63eb1c8e6","tid":1025333,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1055019201356814/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1055019201356814%2F&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=7e7b5d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1055019201356814/</a><br />\n<br />\n【所羅門群島海域】<br />\n【尋獲二戰日艦比叡號】<br />\n<br />\n微軟創辦人之一 Paul Allen (保羅艾倫) 生前創立的海底搜索隊，在所羅門群島海域一千公尺深的海底，發現一艘軍艦殘骸，證實是日本海軍的戰艦比叡號。<br />\n<br />\n在二戰時期，比叡號曾經參與偷襲珍珠港，後來在太平洋戰爭沉沒。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #新聞通識 #二次世界大戰 #日本 #戰艦 #比叡號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女主播索到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0760f06d848fce7cc5dfaef0376f855610088bf","tid":1025333,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWkHesT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWkHesT.gif&h=c45c6f93&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}